    "order": 19
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "docling_exam_paper_en-file-putnam-archive_2010_Solutions_2010s_page_001_26",
    "text": "Proof. If xx y # 0, then y x x is nonzero and distinct from xx y. Consequently, x*y=*xyandy**=yxx#x*y.",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.5169172856729406,
